      "content": {
        "title": "Soft Tissue Sarcoma — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Malignant mesenchymal tumors of soft tissues requiring wide excision often combined with radiation.",
        "summary": "MRI defines compartment and neurovascular involvement. Margin status drives local recurrence. STS subtypes include liposarcoma and synovial sarcoma."
      },
